quran[5]{c,v,t}:
  18,45,"Fakkeenya jiruu addunyaa akka bishaan samii irraa buufnee, biqiltuuwwan dachii isatti makamanii, goggogaa caccabaa bubbeen isa faffacaaftu ta’een godhiifiRabbiin waan hunda irratti danda’aa ta’eera"
  18,46,Qabeenyiifi ilmaan faaya jirreenya addunyaatiGaggaarii haftuu taatetu Gooftaa kee biratti mindaadhaan irra caala; gama abdiittis irra caalaadha
  18,47,"Guyyaa Nuti gaarreen deemsifnee dachiis dirree ta’uu argitee, isaanis walitti qabnu [yaadadhu]Isaan irraas tokkollee hin hanbifnu"
  18,48,"Hiriiroo godhamanii Gooftaa kee irra fidaman; “dhugumatti, akka yeroo jalqabaa isin uumnetti nutti dhuftanNuti waadaa isiniif godhuu dhabuu yaaddu turtan” (jedhaman)"
  18,49,"Galmeenis kaa’amee, yoma san badii raawwattoota waan isa keessa jiru irraa sodaatoo ta’anii isaan agartaNi jedhus: “Yaa badii keenya! Kitaabni kun kan xiqqoofi guddoos ishee walitti qabu malee hin dhiifne maaluma!” Waan hojjatan dhiyaataa ta’ee arguGooftaan kee tokkollee hin miidhu"